version_description:
List of changes: 
- the ability to hide the player error message using the button; 
- updated the mechanism for saving categories of TV channels; 
- fixed a problem that could lead to the continuation of the broadcast when entering the channel list; 
- fixed errors when switching to the "Только звук" output mode, as well as when exiting the "Только звук" mode.

New version key features:
- updated the player aspect ratio switching mode;
- fixed a possible malfunction in the "Sound only" mode after the ad is shown;
- added synchronization of updating the channel list when changing the region or time display in the application settings;
- font size change is now available only through system settings;
- removed the function of swiping channels by swiping;
- disabled the possible launch of the broadcast in the background of the application on an incoming call.

Thank you for using our app!
